::DarkMouse::

"Hey, Scorponok." She realized she sounded a little too excited to hear him 
on her commlink. She cleared her throut and tried to sound as bored as 
possable. "Well, good to hear that your still functioning commander. I need 
your help when you return."
She leaned back in the chair aand gave a big sigh of relief.  She was really 
glad to hear that he was OK and heading back to the base.
Then she sat back and remembered what she had told herself earlier.
"yeah, one snowball's chance in the inferno."
She checked her computer again for systems relays malfuctions and sat back 
and waited for Scorponok to return.
